7. [decision] ADR-011 (OCaml core engine "kern") — still "Proposed". It
   would move the parser Rust -> OCaml, a second migration of a component
   that already moved Go -> Rust (PR #688). Resolving this decides whether
   the engine-layer migration is essentially complete or the parser hops
